        {
            "title": "半日收市︱反覆爭持 恒指半日升83點報26011點 泡泡瑪特急彈曾飆近10%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">外圍股市向好，港股今早在美股感恩節休市前卻只能反覆爭持，近月陷入整固的泡泡瑪特(09992)則在內地出台促消費方案帶動下揚升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早高開17點後，初段先跌後倒升，低位25822點時跌105點，於上午10時過後不久已反彈至半日高位26082點，升154點，其後於26000點上下百多點呈反覆爭持局面；恒指中午收報26011點，升83點或0.32%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"迷你版LABUBU (圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網)\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508028_FI_source-web_09992.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"迷你版LABUBU (圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508028_FI_source-web_09992.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">迷你版LABUBU (圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網)</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"迷你版LABUBU (圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508028_FI_source-web_09992.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">迷你版LABUBU (圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網)</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數相對跑輸，半日升7點或0.13%，報5625點；國企指數升36點或0.4%，報9198點。主板半日成交1171.7億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日升75點，報26006點，低水5點。科指期貨升8點，報5625點，低水1點。國指期貨升25點，報9190點，低水9點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股互有升跌，在「ATMXJ」當中以阿里巴巴(09988)表現較遜，今早進一步回吐，中午收報151.2元，跌2.33%；騰訊(00700)跌0.81%，報614.5元；昨天撐市主力美團(03690)反覆靠穩，中午企於103.8元收市。單是阿里巴巴與騰訊，已拖低恒指逾71點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">相反，小米(01810)則持續反彈，升2.99%，報41.3元，在藍籌升幅榜中排第3位，為恒指提供逾34點進賬。近期傳聞多多的京東(09618)亦再漲2%，報117.1元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩大藍籌國際金融股也是撐市主力，友邦(01299)升1.74%，報82.1元；滙控(00005)升0.93%，報108.6元。兩股亦合共對恒指貢獻近44點升幅。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今早表現最佳藍籌則是泡泡瑪特，該股今早裂口高開0.68%後升幅迅速擴大，最高曾見225元，飆9.97%，其後仍在高位徘徊；該股中午收報222.6元，漲8.8%，也拉高恒指21點，半日交投42.43億元，在主板股份成交額榜上排第3位，僅次於阿里巴巴與騰訊，較小米則略為領先。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">發改委等內地6大部委昨午印發《關於增強消費品供需適配性進一步促進消費的實施方案》，表明拓展多元興趣消費供給，積極發展寵物周邊、動漫、潮服潮玩等興趣消費產品。近年以LABUBU備受大眾關注的泡泡瑪特，遂借勢炒上。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"迷你版LABUBU (圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508028_FI_source-web_09992.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"迷你版LABUBU (圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508028_FI_source-web_09992.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">迷你版LABUBU (圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網)</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">不少內地消費類股份亦造好，藍籌股當中，蒙牛乳業(02319)升2.45%，報15.07元；華潤啤酒(00291)漲2.29%，報27.68元；百威亞太(01876)升1.75%，報8.12元；安踏(02020)也升1.72%，報85.7元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">非藍籌消費板塊中，名創優品(09896)升4.09%，報39.7元；老鋪黃金(06181)升2.26%，報655.5元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，科技新聞網站The Information引述字節跳動員工指，內地監管機構禁止該公司在新數據中心使用英偉達(Nvidia)晶片。有關消息推動國產芯片股應聲造好，中芯國際(00981)升1.09%，報69.6元；華虹半導體(01347)升1.24%，報73.7元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-142322_source-web_00981.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">理想汽車(02015)昨天收市後公布業績，上季由盈轉虧，但該股今早卻反覆造好，最低報71.4元，僅微跌0.42%；中午收報72.55元，升1.19%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">「蔚小理」其餘兩成員則個別發展，績後於昨天捱沽的蔚來(09866)，今早再跌1.46%，報43.26元；早前已派成績表的小鵬汽車(09868)則升1.89%，報83.65元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新股方面，羊小咩母公司量化派(02685)今早登場，以26元開市，較招股價9.8元高1.65倍；中午收報20.9元，仍較招股價高1.13倍，半日成交1.07億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15461052-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8f%8d%e8%a6%86%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%8783%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126011%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b3%a1%e6%b3%a1%e7%91%aa%e7%89%b9",
